on / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Ma7GBn&quot;>;Google 即将推出的 Pixel 手机可能会配备升级版 Tensor 芯片，该芯片可支持多项新的 AI 功能，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.androidauthority.com/google-pixel-10-and-pixel-11-camera-ai-features-3494468/&quot;>;Android Authority 看到的泄露文档&lt;/em>;&lt;/一个>;。据报道，Pixel 11 的一项功能包括更先进的 Pixel 设备端版本 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24012568/google-pixel-8-pro-video-boost-ai -photos&quot;>;具有夜视功能的视频增强&lt;/a>;，可提高在黑暗中拍摄的视频的亮度。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;fZek0N&quot;>;Pixel 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs. net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://store.google.com/intl/en/ideas/articles/night-sight-video/&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank &quot;>;现有的低光功能&lt;/a>;使用人工智能自动调整视频的曝光、稳定视频并减少颗粒感。我的同事 Allison Johnson 在 Pixel 8 Pro 上进行了尝试，发现&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24012568/google-pixel-8-pro-video-boost-ai-photos&quot; >;效果很好&lt;/a>;。要提高 Pixel 9 上的视频亮度，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://store.google.com/intl/en/ ideas/articles/night-sight-video/&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Google 结合使用设备端处理和基于云的处理&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;jmMnnE&quot;>;Pixel 11 传闻中的“超低光视频”...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10 /28/24281679/google-pixel-10-11-leak-ai-features-rumors&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24281679/google-pixel-10-11-leak-ai-features-rumors" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24281679/google-pixel-10-11-leak-ai-features-rumors</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-28T11:42:23-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-28T11:42:23-04:00</updated><title>苹果再次将Magic Mouse的充电口放在底部</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;USB-C 妙控鼠标的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0MDmufyvXUzr-lAR4YJxyHruWco=/99x0:1590x994/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73683745/Screenshot_2024_10_28_at_11.33.03 _AM.0 .png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;是的，它还在那里。 |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;An3iHv&quot;>;Apple 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24275569/apple-usb-c-magic -keyboard-mouse-trackpad-no-lightning&quot;>;配备 USB-C 的新款 Magic Mouse&lt;/a>; 不知怎的，充电端口仍然位于底部。虽然苹果本可以利用这次发布作为机会，将充电端口从设备底部移开——尽管 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/ 3/8/22967472/apple-black-magic-trackpad-peripherals-mouse-charging&quot;>;其他&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/4/20/22394034/apple -new-imac-m1-chip-colors-design-specs-price-release-date&quot;>;更新&lt;/a>;鼠标和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/4/ 20/22394552/apple-new-magic-mouse-charging-port-bottom-lightning&quot;>;正在&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22967776/apple-magic-mouse-charging -port-bottom-upside-down-its-2022&quot;>;嘲笑&lt;/a>;这个决定 - 端口仍然在那里。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;kH8qJS&quot;>;这个&lt;a href=&quot;https:// /apple.sjv.io/c/482924/1683292/7613?subId1=veergeappleproducts102824&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FMXK63AM%2FA%2Fmagic-mouse-usb%25E2%2580 %2591c-black-multi-touch-surface&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;新款 99 美元 Magic Mouse&lt;/a>; 意味着，在可预见的未来，Apple 仍然认为为您的设备充电的最佳方式Magic Mouse 是通过翻转它来插入它，从而使您无法使用它。为什么？&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;04zeRe&quot;>;还有其他解决方案来解决可笑的 Magic Mouse 充电问题。例如，我的同事 Wes Davis 写了一篇有关 Magic Mouse 2 符合人体工程学的握把的文章，它可以 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/21/24045324/apple-magic-mouse-wireless- charging-lightning-base&quot;>;充电...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24276043/apple-new- usb-c-magic-mouse-charging-port-bottom&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24276043/apple-new-usb-c-magic-mouse-charging-port-bottom" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24276043/apple-new-usb-c-magic-mouse-charging-port-bottom</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-28T11:34:01-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-28T11:34:01-04:00</updated><title>谷歌可能会在 Pixel Watch 5 中安装 Tensor 芯片</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;45mm Pixel Watch 3 特写&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Iv-qpa2dwfzj7JNFqUJwIMLrFzA=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73683725/247234_Pixel_Watch_3_AKrales_0114.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;泄露的详细信息暗示 Google 可能会在 2026 年推出定制可穿戴 Tensor 芯片。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;8TeMBe&quot;>;从 2026 年开始，Google 可能会为 Pixel Watch 5 配备定制 Tensor 处理器。 &lt;/p>; &lt; p id=&quot;rYIsyK&quot;>;谣言来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.androidauthority.com/google-pixel-watch-5-tensor-chip-3494524/&quot;>;&lt;em>;Android Authority&lt;/ em>;&lt;/a>;，其中引用了 Google gChips 部门泄露的文件。根据泄露的计划，这款可穿戴 Tensor 芯片代号为 NPT，核心配置为 ARM Cortex A78 和两颗 Arm Cortex A55。这些是较旧的 CPU 内核，但这是可穿戴处理器的相当典型的举动。除此之外，细节很少，目前尚不清楚计划中的可穿戴 Tensor 芯片可能采用哪种工艺节点技术。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;YeGASU&quot;>;芯片通常不像智能手表那样受到重视。智能手机。只要性能出色，智能手表制造商往往会专注于延长时间的方法...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24281712/google -pixel-watch-5-tensor-chips-smartwatches-wearables&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24281712/google-pixel-watch-5-tensor-chips-smartwatches-wearables" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/28/24281712/google-pixel-watch-5-tensor-chips-smartwatches-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-28T11:22:11-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-28T11:22:11-04:00</updated><title>龙腾世纪：面纱卫士开始缓慢但强劲</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;视频游戏《龙腾世纪：面纱卫士》的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Y